omic handle to provide comfort during use; Soft foam wrap adds grip and helps prevent slippage to protect your inner palm and wrist while gardening and planting</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">DURABLE CONSTRUCTION - All hand tools have a wooden handle with steelhead construction to ensure a long service life; Materials are water-resistant so you can garden rain or shine; Rinse and dry garden cultivator tools once done and store in a dry place to increase longevity</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">SPECIFICATIONS - Materials: wood (handle); steel (tool head); Color: black; Set size: 3 pieces (cultivator, rake, shovel); Soft foam grip wrap on handle</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody>\n\t\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t\t</div><!-- /product-specs -->\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t<h1>ToolTreaux Wooden Steel Handheld Garden Tools Set Rake Shovel Cultivator&nbsp;</h1>\n\t\t\t<h2>MSRP <span class=\"msrp-strike\">14.99</span></h2>\n\t\t\t<p>Are you an avid gardener or just getting started? This set of 3 handheld gardening tools from ToolTreaux comes with 3 essential tools used to remove garden debris, as well as to level and grade your garden soil before plants or seeds are planted in your garden, herb garden, flowerpot, plant pot, or succulent planter.\n\nInside this set, you’ll find 3 common gardening tools that every gardener needs to ensure they have a healthy garden: a hoe, a rake, and a shovel/trowel. These tools are specifically designed to help dig, plant, and cultivate your garden. The hoe is perfect for weeding and chopping soil, the rake for leveling and grading, and the shovel for digging and aerating.\n\nAll 3 of our gardening tools feature an ergonomic handle to provide comfort during use, and the soft foam wrap adds grip and helps prevent slippage to protect your inner palm and wrist while gardening and planting. The tools themselves are made of steel to ensure a long service life, and the materials are weather-resistant so you can garden rain or shine. \n\nTo properly clean your garden tools, just rinse them and dry them once done and store them in a dry place to increase longevity. Whether you’re an experienced gardener or trying a new hobby, this is a must-have set of essential gardening tools!</p>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"d-flex d-flex-col grid-60 center text-center bg-grey\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-header m-all-1rem all-caps\">Newsletter</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-100\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>SUBSCRIBE for Early Access to Sales</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Up to 90% Off</p>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-80 center\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"newsletter-link\" href=\"https://my.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?AcceptSavedSeller&amp;sellerid=dealsonlywebstore\" target=\"_blank\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-btn all-caps\">Sign Up</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div><!-- /col-md-6 -->\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12 footer\">\n\t\t\t<p>© 2025</p></div></div>",
